rComments: Kim is an ok prof, but she talks a lot and loves to hear herself speak. It's like you can't get a word in even during questions and comments and will often cut you off. That being said her lectures are very dynamic and she's no doubt very coherent and a real feminist !

La matière est intéressante, mais c'est vraiment Kim qui rend ça facile et fun! Ses powerpoints sont rempli avec toute la matière, mais elle ajoute des exemples personnelles pour bien illustrer. Les discussions en classe sont encouragées et très intéressantes! Prenez ce cours si vous avez la chance! Vous allez tout questionner, ça vaut la peine!

Kim is an amazing prof! She goes above and beyond for her students and she makes sure that everyone is on the same page! Attendance is not mandatory as she fills up her power points pretty good, but she will notice if you're not there! She is approachable, kind, funny and passionnate! The course itself is average, the prof is great!
